  "response": "To provide insights about your birth chart regarding your future, including career and marriage, it's essential to know your birth date, birth time, and birth location. These details help in creating your natal chart, which is a map of the sky at the moment of your birth and it\u2019s pivotal for astrological readings.\n\nOnce you provide this information, I'll be able to present a generalized analysis. However, please note that for a more comprehensive and personalized reading, visiting a professional astrologer who can interpret the nuances of your natal chart would be recommended.",
